@startuml
title Sequence (Stakeholder) - Drop Course

actor Student
participant "University Course Registration System" as System
actor "Academic Advisor" as Advisor
participant "Refund Service" as Refund

Student -> System: Log in and open schedule
System --> Student: Display current enrollments

Student -> System: Request to drop course
System -> System: Check drop deadline,\nfinancial holds, and policy

alt Not eligible to drop
  System --> Student: Cannot drop course\n(deadline passed / hold / policy)
else Eligible to drop
  System -> Advisor: Notify / request approval\n(if required by program)
  Advisor --> System: Approve or reject

  alt Approved
    System -> Refund: Request refund\n(if eligible)
    Refund --> System: Refund issued / not eligible
    System --> Student: Course dropped\n+ refund info (if any)
  else Rejected
    System --> Student: Drop request rejected\nwith reason
  end
end

@enduml